{
  "stem": "9995.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] There were no rationing whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have a little money, you could buy some food in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, we were in the position that my mother was once in a while selling a ring or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and also she was, what I think, all those applications for different thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now I, believe it or not, I was making a little money by being a dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And since I was very skillful, I was making a little money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were not-- unlike very many other people, we were not destitute.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, my grandfather, who had money because he and one of his daughter, my aunt, were collecting gold money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they had $20 in gold, francs in gold, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And once they were selling one piece, they could live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But whoever had some money, they were coming at nighttime and at that time already, taking them to Auschwitz, although still not throwing people out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So grandfather, who was at that time 84 years old-- was-- there was not much coal to warm the apartment, but there was wood.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was chopping wood, actually, at this age, because he was so afraid that somebody will say he has reputation as being wealthy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he said to everybody, well, I lost my business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I lost my income from houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I lost everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I have nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They did not know that he still had a lot of jewelry and those gold pieces, which were a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so he was actually going-- at his age-- he didn't look his age.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He had 20/20 vision, no wrinkles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, his great grandfather lived to be 113, so he had some good genes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it was heartbreaking when I saw my grandfather going from house to house and chopping wood.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
